# .claude Configuration Reference (Sanitized)

This file is a sanitized reference snapshot of the project `.claude/` directory.
Replace placeholders such as `YOUR_TOKEN` and `<PROJECT_PATH>` with local values
when adapting these examples.

## File Tree

```text
.claude/
  settings.local.json
  settings.likecode.local.json
  settings.likecode.local copy.json
  skills/
    constraint-driven-exploration/
      SKILL.md
```

